merhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片11-e1411032833361.jpg\" alt=\"图片1\" width=\"500\" height=\"571\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片2-e1411033027768.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-331\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片2-e1411033027768.jpg\" alt=\"图片2\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">蓝天，白云，仪式堂，AYANA见证你们的幸福瞬间。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片3-e1411033085482.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-332\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片3-e1411033085482.jpg\" alt=\"图片3\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片4-e1411033104722.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片4-e1411033104722.jpg\" alt=\"图片4\" width=\"500\" height=\"384\" /></a></p>\r\n一袭洁白的婚纱如同单纯可爱的你，美到无法形容。步入人生另一个阶段的新娘，DREAMER给您最大的祝福。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片6-e1411033332281.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-348\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片6-e1411033332281.jpg\" alt=\"图片6\" width=\"541\" height=\"722\" /></a>\r\n\r\n我们牵手，一辈子。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片7-e1411033267320.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-336\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片7-e1411033267320.jpg\" alt=\"图片7\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" /></a>\r\n\r\n神父握着新人的手，开始宣读誓词。你，愿意吗？\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片8-e1411033420314.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片8-e1411033420314.jpg\" alt=\"图片8\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" /></a>\r\n\r\n在场的亲友，忍不住落泪-----因感动而落泪。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片9-e1411033456856.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-338\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片9-e1411033456856.jpg\" alt=\"图片9\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" /></a>\r\n\r\nDREAMER谢谢新人如此信任我们的团队，谢谢你们的幸福感染了所有人。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片10-e1411033484132.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-339\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片10-e1411033484132.jpg\" alt=\"图片10\" width=\"499\" height=\"748\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n神圣美好的婚礼圆满结束后，接下来是专属于新人2人的浪漫晚宴。私人海滩，玉桂晚宴，蜡烛微光，在漫天繁星下细说爱情。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片111-e1411033568949.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-350\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片111-e1411033568949.jpg\" alt=\"图片11\" width=\"502\" height=\"343\" /></a>\r\n\r\n新人觉得晚宴太美，一直自拍不肯入座，太可爱了！\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片12-e1411033603770.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片12-e1411033603770.jpg\" alt=\"图片12\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片13-e1411033618361.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-341\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片13-e1411033618361.jpg\" alt=\"图片13\" width=\"500\" height=\"410\" /></a>\r\n\r\nROCK BAR相拥，见证海枯石烂的爱情。无论在哪里，你都是我最爱的人。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片14-e1411033662605.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-342\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片14-e1411033662605.jpg\" alt=\"图片14\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href