rc=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片41.jpg\" alt=\"图片4\" width=\"782\" height=\"522\" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n“我终于等到你了！”\n\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7158.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7158.jpg\" alt=\"7158\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7159.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-398\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7159.jpg\" alt=\"7159\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7157.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-394\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7157.jpg\" alt=\"7157\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\n\n“是的，我愿意。”\n\n&nbsp;\n\n“你的名字，我的姓氏，蓝天白云见证，你永远是我的家人！”\n\n&nbsp;\n\n亲友的见证，唱诗班的伴唱，空气中飘着小黄花的香甜气息，新郎新娘拥吻，这是婚礼最美好的见证。\n\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7152.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-388\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7152.jpg\" alt=\"7152\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\n\n“抛花球咯，接着！”所有人都沉浸在这欢乐的气氛中，谁会是下一位呢？\n\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/715.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-383 size-full\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/715.jpg\" alt=\"715\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7151.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-386\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7151.jpg\" alt=\"7151\" width=\"4877\" height=\"3239\" /></a>8\n\n“我与你在崖边拥吻，享受夕阳的温柔。”\n\n晚宴是家庭欢聚的时光，DREAMER希望这样的安排能让大家都感受到满满的幸福！\n\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7153.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-390\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/u