=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片51.jpg\" alt=\"图片5\" width=\"1269\" height=\"845\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片61.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-408\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片61.jpg\" alt=\"图片6\" width=\"560\" height=\"840\" /></a>\r\n\r\n“我终于等到你了！”\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7158.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7158.jpg\" alt=\"7158\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7159.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-398\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7159.jpg\" alt=\"7159\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7157.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-394\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7157.jpg\" alt=\"7157\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\r\n\r\n“是的，我愿意。”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n“你的名字，我的姓氏，蓝天白云见证，你永远是我的家人！”\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片71.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-410\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片71.jpg\" alt=\"图片7\" width=\"741\" height=\"494\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片81.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-411\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片81.jpg\" alt=\"图片8\" width=\"742\" height=\"495\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片91.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-412\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片91.jpg\" alt=\"图片9\" width=\"742\" height=\"495\" /></a>\r\n\r\n亲友的见证，唱诗班的伴唱，空气中飘着小黄花的香甜气息，新郎新娘拥吻，这是婚礼最美好的见证。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7152.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-388\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7152.jpg\" alt=\"7152\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\r\n\r\n“抛花球咯，接着！”所有人都沉浸在这欢乐的气氛中，谁会是下一位呢？\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/715.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-383 size-full\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/715.jpg\" alt=\"715\" width=\"5760\" height=\"3840\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7151.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-386\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7151.jpg\" alt=\"7151\" width=\"4877\" height=\"3239\" /></a>8\r\n\r\n“我与你在崖边拥吻，享受夕阳的温柔。”\r\n\r\n晚宴是家庭欢聚的时光，DREAMER希望这样的安排能让大家都感受到满满的幸福！\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7153.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-390\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7153.jpg\" alt=\"7153\" width=\"5251\" height=\"3501\" /></a>\r\n\r\n“在月光下与你共舞，我才知道什么叫美好。”太唯美的画面，DREAMER忍不住按下了快门。愿你们的爱，永远在巴厘岛的夜空中闪耀着。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7154.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-392\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/7154.jpg\" alt=\"7154\" width=\"5608\" height=\"3739\" /></a>','水之教堂婚礼','','inherit','open','open','','373-revision-v1','','','2014-09-29 15:15:32','2014-09-29 07:15:32','',373,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/?p=479',0,'revision','',0),(480,1,'2014-09-29 15:23:50','2014-09-29 07:23:50','在白马婚车上，一路牵手凝视对方------胶片定格在这一刻------DREAMER希望你们永远幸福下去。 三个月前，DREAMER与新人相识，听着他们的故事，看着他们彼此间默契的笑容，DREAMER感到深深的幸福。经过一系列的筹备，三个月后，DREAMER与新人共同踏上了巴厘岛这个神圣之地。踩点，布置，凌晨讨论工作流程，DREAMER承诺：给你一个最美最难忘的婚礼！ 7月11日的巴厘岛,阳光温婉,微风写意,新人在AYANA教堂举行婚礼。新郎在仪式坛前紧张踱步,新娘在父亲的陪伴下徐徐走进教堂，两位新人在神父的主婚下宣读誓词,父母双双拥抱时感动落泪..........每一个瞬间都是婚礼中最夺目最珍贵的点缀。 多年后，DREAMER希望你们的回忆里还有那个悬崖边，教堂里，互相许下誓言的爱情故事。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片11-e1411032833361.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-330\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片11-e1411032833361.jpg\" alt=\"图片1\" width=\"500\" height=\"571\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片2-e1411033027768.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-331\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片2-e1411033027768.jpg\" alt=\"图片2\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">蓝天，白云，仪式堂，AYANA见证你们的幸福瞬间。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片3-e1411033085482.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-332\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片3-e1411033085482.jpg\" alt=\"图片3\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片4-e1411033104722.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片4-e1411033104722.jpg\" alt=\"图片4\" width=\"500\" height=\"384\" /></a></p>\r\n一袭洁白的婚纱如同单纯可爱的你，美到无法形容。步入人生另一个阶段的新娘，DREAMER给您最大的祝福。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片6-e1411033332281.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-348\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片6-e1411033332281.jpg\" alt=\"图片6\" width=\"541\" height=\"722\" /></a>\r\n\r\n我们牵手，一辈子。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片7-e1411033267320.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-336\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片7-e1411033267320.jpg\" alt=\"图片7\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" /></a>\r\n\r\n神父握着新人的手，开始宣读誓词。你，愿意吗？\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片8-e1411033420314.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片8-e1411033420314.jpg\" alt=\"图片8\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" /></a>\r\n\r\n在场的亲友，忍不住落泪-----因感动而落泪。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片9-e1411033456856.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-338\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片9-e1411033456856.jpg\" alt=\"图片9\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" /></a>\r\n\r\nDREAMER谢谢新人如此信任我们的团队，谢谢你们的幸福感染了所有人。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片10-e1411033484132.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-339\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片10-e1411033484132.jpg\" alt=\"图片10\" width=\"499\" height=\"748\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n神圣美好的婚礼圆满结束后，接下来是专属于新人2人的浪漫晚宴。私人海滩，玉桂晚宴，蜡烛微光，在漫天繁星下细说爱情。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片111-e1411033568949.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-350\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片111-e1411033568949.jpg\" alt=\"图片11\" width=\"502\" height=\"343\" /></a>\r\n\r\n新人觉得晚宴太美，一直自拍不肯入座，太可爱了！\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片12-e1411033603770.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片12-e1411033603770.jpg\" alt=\"图片12\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片13-e1411033618361.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-341\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片13-e1411033618361.jpg\" alt=\"图片13\" width=\"500\" height=\"410\" /></a>\r\n\r\nROCK BAR相拥，见证海枯石烂的爱情。无论在哪里，你都是我最爱的人。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片14-e1411033662605.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-342\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片14-e1411033662605.jpg\" alt=\"图片14\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片15-e1411033678621.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片15-e1411033678621.jpg\" alt=\"图片15\" width=\"500\" height=\"396\" /></a>\r\n\r\n第一场完美的巴厘岛婚礼，谢谢新人的信任，谢谢各团队的努力，谢谢你们！\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片17-e1411033703496.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-345\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片17-e1411033703496.jpg\" alt=\"图片17\" width=\"500\" height=\"363\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片18-e1411033718905.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-346\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片18-e1411033718905.jpg\" alt=\"图片18\" width=\"500\" height=\"888\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','AYANA教堂婚礼','','inherit','open','open','','329-revision-v1','','','2014-09-29 15:23:50','2014-09-29 07:23:50','',329,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/?p=480',0,'revision','',0),(481,1,'2014-09-29 15:27:40','2014-09-29 07:27:40','','Dreamer梦想家海外婚礼7月巴厘岛婚礼预告','','publish','open','open','','dreamer%e6%a2%a6%e6%83%b3%e5%ae%b6%e6%b5%b7%e5%a4%96%e5%a9%9a%e7%a4%bc7%e6%9c%88%e5%b7%b4%e5%8e%98%e5%b2%9b%e5%a9%9a%e7%a4%bc%e9%a2%84%e5%91%8a','','','2014-09-30 14:34:12','2014-09-30 06:34:12','',0,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/?p=481',0,'post','',0),(482,1,'2014-09-29 15:27:40','2014-09-29 07:27:40','','Dreamer梦想家海外婚礼7月巴厘岛婚礼预告','','inherit','open','open','','481-revision-v1','','','2014-09-29 15:27:40','2014-09-29 07:27:40','',481,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/?p=482',0,'revision','',0),(483,1,'2014-09-29 15:32:45','2014-09-29 07:32:45','7年前，你遇见了谁？\r\n\r\n7年前的相遇，是甜蜜，还是心里的悸动？\r\n\r\n2006年11月，大学的舞蹈室内，他们初次见面。在最纯真的年代相爱，在社会的种种历练下，他们的爱依然是彼此最坚实的后盾。\r\n\r\n7年后，巴厘岛AYANA教堂，蓝与白为这